{
  "stem": "17761.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I think it was already a kind of a Republican government.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But I'm not sure about that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "In any case, during these few days that they-- they occupied the-- the-- radio station and some other public buildings in Bucharest.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They had a pogrom in Bucharest where a few hundred Jews were killed, and in many other places.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I jump a little bit over because of that question.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But in-- in our city during the [INAUDIBLE] in our town, they gathered all Jews between 18 and 50 in the courtyard of the synagogue and they put around [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] fire-- [NON-ENGLISH], guns, automatic guns.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I won't forget the night that was the night where my grandfather was elder than 70 years.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He-- than 60-- than 50 years.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And he was not brought into that courtyard.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "He called me and he asked me if I could sneak in-- into the courtyard of the synagogue to bring something to my-- to his children.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "He had three children at that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Because I had studied in that cheder, I knew exactly how to get in and how to get out.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I succeeded to get in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And he-- I did what I had to do and I went out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "We didn't know what would be the end of this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "They were really supposed to be exterminated somehow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Fortunately enough, in our place lived a Jew in the name-- his name was Nathan Klipper, N-A-T-H-A-N, Klipper, K-L-I-P-P-E-R, who was a non-religious Jew that had little-- little relationship with the synagogues in the-- in our place.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "But he was a wonderful Jewish person.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And he had some-- he dealt with German officers, because he-- he was in the wood-- wood industry.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And he had some business with German officers.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
